LGBT Data Visualization

Justin Pimentel and Joseph Snitzer

5/16/2020

With Here

data <- read.csv(here::here("data/travel.csv"))

ggplot(data) + geom_point(aes(x=ZipCode, y=MEAN_Total_Time))
## Warning: Removed 1 rows containing missing values (geom_point).

Without Here

ggplot(data) + geom_point(aes(x=ZipCode, y=MEAN_Total_Time))
